parameters: There were various troubles, but all in all, it was fun, wasn't it?♪
That's right♪ Next time we come, maybe the kids will be with us♪
Geez♪ Tak-kun, you're such a tease♪

I don't often come to the park at night, so it feels a bit scary
compared to usual...

Right? How about we try the alcohol I bought from the convenience
store earlier?
Drinking outside once in a while isn't too bad, I think♪
How about we do it here?

Come on... wake up... if you sleep here, you'll catch a cold, you
know?
Huh...? Did I... pee while Tak-kun was holding me...
Ah... huh? What was I doing?
You drank the alcohol I bought and then just fell asleep, didn't you?♪
Ah... now that you mention it... I kind of feel like that happened...

What... it was a dream... right, of course... doing it in a place like
this...
I'm sorry for drinking the alcohol... it seems like I did...
I'll buy some more later, so it's fine♪
I wonder what it's like inside the school now...
Hmm... I might be a little curious...
I do have a school uniform... Maybe I should sneak in wearing it...
No... No way!! That would be trespassing!!

But... but... it's Akane's school, and as a guardian, I might need to
check on it...
No way!! As a guardian, I need to see for myself!
Yeah! Yeah! This is necessary, right?!
I'll just change into the uniform behind here♪
Mmm...♪ The breeze feels so nice～♪
It's been a while since I've been on a school rooftop♪

Walking around the school like this brings back memories of my student
days...
Oops... I shouldn't... I'm getting too relaxed...

If I don't panic and blend in with the surroundings, I can still pass
for a student!
Ah~ If only Tak-kun were here with me~
I did come to Akane's school, but...
Ugh... It's a bit embarrassing maybe...
Eh? You're leaving already? We just got here...

We've come all this way to Akane-chan's school, let's enjoy it a
little more♪
Enjoy it? How are we supposed to do that?

But... if Tak-kun wants me to wear it, I don't mind doing it while
dressed up...

Who is that person over there... Smiling to themselves, it's kind of
creepy...
A teacher from this school, maybe?
Eh? A teacher? A teacher wouldn't wear a school uniform...
Ah! Maybe they're a student who had to repeat a year?
In that case, isn't it better not to get involved too much?
Y...Yes... Let's just leave them be...
Phew... I managed to sneak out of the school, but...
I...It's not really good to play pranks like this, is it...
If Akane finds out, it'll be trouble, so let's stop doing this...
Huh? I didn't know there was a park here...
It's a small park, but it even has a toilet installed...
Hmm? It seems like someone is here... Maybe a little kid is playing?
Welcome~♪ What can I get for you?
Water, coming right up~♪ Please wait just a moment♪
Ahh~n♪ A little kid is playing house♪
Sigh... How nice♪ I wish I could have kids soon too...
Eh!? Could it be me you're talking about!?
Aren't you a customer, big sis?

Wha... What should I do... I was so surprised when she suddenly
started talking to me...
I guess I'll just play along for now...
Yeah♪ I heard there was a shop here, so I thought I'd check it out♪
If you're a customer, please come this way~♪
Customer♪ What would you like to order~?

Hana-chan♪ Since an adult big sis came in, let's have this big sis be
the manager♪
Ah! That's right♪ That sounds good♪
Big sis! Be the manager-chan, please♪
Eh!? Big sis is going to be the manager?
This is troubling... Big sis... I've never been a shop clerk before...

It's okay♪ All you have to do is listen to the customer's order and
make it♪
So then... what would you like to order♪
Eh!? Lemon juice? We don't have that here?
Ehh~!? But we do, right? It comes out from your crotch, doesn't it?
Yep♪ Pee! When we make lemon juice, everyone uses pee to make it♪

No way... Tha... Tha... That's not okay!! You can't make lemon juice
with pee!
It's fine♪ We have containers for it right here♪
It's not about the container! We can't just pee here...
If you don't make it quickly, the customers will get angry!
Be careful not to spill it!
Even if you say you want it, I can't produce that much~
The lemon juice is limited in quantity, so we only sell one per day♪
Yay♪ Big sis's hot lemon juice♪
It's not fair just for Hana-chan!! Let me carry some too!!
It's a strange feeling to have my pee carried around by someone...
Yeah, yeah... that's right... she was happy about it!
This... this might be okay in its own way...
Ahhn! There's no way that's okay!!

It's embarrassing!! I can't tell Tak-kun about such an embarrassing
thing!!
What am I doing!! So stupid, stupid!!
Uuu... I have to keep this incident locked away in my heart...
Wow... there are so many cardboard boxes...
Cardboard boxes come in all sorts of sizes, huh...
The one on top looks like I could fit my whole body inside it...
Are all these... cardboard boxes from a factory, I wonder...
Hmm? What's this? Wandering around here could be dangerous, you know?
I'm from Tomozumi Real Estate, here to inspect the property...
Ah... you're from the real estate agency... that's just perfect.

These cardboard boxes lying around are in the way, can you do
something about them?
Looks like the previous tenants left them here...
Understood. I'll pass the message to the person in charge.
If you give us some time, we will take care of it.
It's quite a lot of cardboard boxes...
Right? It's a hassle when they're just left like this...
It's a shame, they still seem usable...
Huh? You want some cardboard boxes?
Ah... no, it's not that I want them...

If you want some cardboard boxes, feel free to take them. They're just
going to be trash anyway.
Alright then! I'm counting on you.
I wonder if I can use these cardboard boxes for something...
I just had a great idea!
I'll take you up on that offer and take just one with me.
I can't believe I got noticed...
Well... I guess there is a smell... Sorry, Momone...
It's not your fault, Takkun♪ Don't worry about it♪

Now that I think about it, Mom asked me to do something while she's on
her trip...
What? Did Mom ask you to do something?
She asked me to check on Akane's situation from time to time...

Akane-chan is pretty reliable, isn't she? I don't think there's any
need to worry.
Geez! Tak-kun, you're always so soft on Akane!
If you're worried, shall we stop by?
Mmm... It's not that I'm worried, but...
Since Mom told me to, I have to go check on her...
She might be wasting money or something...
Hmm? I wonder who that is...
Ah... Akane... What's up at this hour?

Sorry! I forgot something at home!! Could you please bring it to the
academy for me?
It's something important, right? You can't forget it again, okay?
Yes~♪ I'll be careful~♪ See you~♪
If I wear the uniform, maybe I can get inside...
Maybe I'll sneak in for a bit♪

Hehehe♪ I'll change into the uniform behind there and take a look
around inside♪

Being able to enter the academy in a uniform means I must still look
young♪
I'll take this chance to look around Akane's academy♪
Hmm? Isn't that Akane over there...
I wonder what she's doing at the academy pool...

Hmm... There are boys with her, maybe they're doing some warm-up
exercises together...
I'll sneak a peek to see if Akane is leading a proper school life♪
Come on, hurry up!! The thirty thousand yen you promised!!

Um... Sorry... Can we settle it after I get back to the classroom? I
don't have my wallet with me in this outfit...
Really... You should carry your wallet with you...
That... How much would it be for that other thing...
That side? What do you mean by 'that side'...
Hah!? You mean you want to do the real thing with me!?

Akane-chan is always so prickly, but she's smart and kind... and cute
too...
I've thought so for a long time...
I'm not happy to hear that at all!

Plus, I'm not interested in a gloomy guy who tries to buy girls with
money
How about a hundred thousand yen...?
We... Well... if it's with a condom...

More importantly, hurry up and get dressed! We're going to the
classroom!
Ah... Akane, what are you doing!!
Improper relations with the opposite sex are not allowed!
I should scold her firmly as her sister...
But I'd like to say that...

I'm sneaking into the school in my uniform, so I'm not really in a
position to lecture anyone...
If she questions why I'm here, I'll be the one in trouble...

Ooh... I guess I have no choice but to keep quiet about this
incident...
Sigh... I'll pretend I didn't see anything and go home...
That's right... I need to remind Akane to study...
Since I'm already here, I might as well drop by Akane's place...
I wonder if she's not home...
Darn it... I left the house key back at home...
Sigh... It's such a hassle to go back and get it...
Akane... she wouldn't be pretending to be out, would she...?
Maybe I'll take a little peek inside...
This is no place to be checking on studies...

*sigh*... Let's just pretend we didn't see that and go home for
today...
I've been wandering around and ended up near my parents' house...
Since I'm here, maybe I'll check if Akane is studying properly...
Though she's probably just lazing around in her room...
